<view class="page">
  <view class="tips" wx:if="{{useFallback}}">
    当前展示本地缓存进展，连接后端后可查看实时数据。
  </view>

  <scroll-view scroll-x class="status-scroll">
    <view class="status-row">
      <view
        wx:for="{{statusOptions}}"
        wx:key="value"
        class="status-chip {{activeStatus === item.value ? 'active' : ''}}"
        data-status="{{item.value}}"
        bindtap="onFilterTap"
      >
        {{item.label}}
      </view>
    </view>
  </scroll-view>

  <view class="alert-section" wx:if="{{alertList.length > 0}}">
    <view class="section-title">最新变更提醒</view>
    <view class="alert-item" wx:for="{{alertList}}" wx:key="id">
      <view class="alert-title-row">
        <text class="alert-title">{{item.title}}</text>
        <text class="confidence {{item.confidenceLabel}}">{{item.confidenceLabel || 'medium'}}</text>
      </view>
      <text class="alert-content">{{item.content}}</text>
      <text class="alert-time">{{item.scheduledAtText}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-title">我的申请进展</view>
  <view class="empty" wx:if="{{progressList.length === 0}}">
    <text>还没有申请进展，先去夏令营详情页点击“加入申请进展”。</text>
    <button class="primary-btn" bindtap="onOpenCampList">去看夏令营</button>
  </view>

  <view class="progress-list" wx:else>
    <view
      class="progress-item"
      wx:for="{{progressList}}"
      wx:key="id"
      data-id="{{item.id}}"
      bindtap="onOpenProgressDetail"
    >
      <view class="row">
        <text class="title">{{item.campTitle}}</text>
        <text class="status">{{item.statusText}}</text>
      </view>
      <view class="meta-row">
        <text>{{item.universityName}}</text>
        <text>截止: {{item.deadlineText}}</text>
      </view>
      <text class="next-action">下一步: {{item.nextAction}}</text>
      <view class="meta-row">
        <text>更新于 {{item.updatedAtText}}</text>
        <text>{{item.subscriptionEnabled ? '已订阅变更' : '未订阅变更'}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
